IMPORTANT: Precisions about Notifications and user

  Actually, the web application don't send email because I didn't create
  daemon and threading system in order to check regularly currencies spot.
  And in order to delete or modify Users informations or Alerts, you have to go
  to the admin section at this address localhost:8000/admin. So you have to
  create a superuser. To do that, start the virtual environment and go to the 
  manage.py location. Then do this:

  shell$ ./manage.py createsuperuser

  Follow the instruction and then you can log yourself in to the admin section
  at the previous address.
